tasks of vital human\neffort.\nChrist came into the world not to\nseparate men from life, but to bring\na larger, richer life into men.\nChrist came into the world to con\nsecrate humanity to a holy priest\nhood, serving God in the ritual of\nthe oommon <life.\ni The activities that mar and weak\nen and destroy humanity, he would\ncheck and .crush out.\nThe activities that develop true\nmanhood and womanhood and make\nthe world a better place to live in\nhe would encourage and enlarge.\nHe came to. break down the false\ndistinction between the sacred and\nthe secular.\nThere is no clean and honest work\nin this world which may not be done\nin 'Christ\u2019s name, and done a little\nbetter because the workman calls\nJesus his Master.\n\u201cEvery mason in the quarry, every\nj\nREADING the signs, they plainly indicate, that the\nbusiness depression cf the\u2018past two, years is periqa-/\nnently behind us. r j\nBusiness in general assumes a decidedly more optim\nistic outlook, and the business man with vision is al\nready carefully laying his platt^for the business revival\nthat is practically upon us. i\nOne of the first and most important actions should\nbe your association with the BjLNK that is in a position\nto best serve your requirement* from a financial stand\npoint.\n\n:(\u00a3wm\n\n\u201e,v...........\no\u00a3&txim$ \u00ab:f;\nm^f.:\ni. t-v,\nVogue Furniture Co.\nINCORPORATED\nV\nI\nr;-\nNow Occupying the Entire Store at\n1612 MAIN STREET\nI And will carry at all times a complete line of new and\nup-to-date Furniture and Housefumishings.\nCOME AND SEE US.\n1\nYou are cordially invited to call And look over our new\nyw We give Green Trading Stamps with every pur\nchase.\nWe will continue our qualify Hemstitching.\nPicoting and Button Covering Department\u2014\nand bur Sewing Machine Repairing.\n\u201cWE FURNISH THE HQME FOR LESS.\u201d\nCASH OR TERMS.\n1612 Main Street Phone 3460\nCOLUMBIA, S. C.\nEnterprise Hardware Co\n1324 Main Street.\nColumbia, S. C.\nSe